originalText.text: The only way to describe the way we feel about the images that you created for us is “awe struck”. We have seen Icelandic glaciers and waterfalls, the Taj Mahal and gardens in India, all of the art that France and Italy have to offer. But, those things are a distant second to what Pye and his Lin and Jirsa team have created for us. The images capture a real piece of what we are, and we will cherish them forever. Thank you and your team for everything you have done for us, and we are looking forward to deciding what to do with these images. We are also talking about our next endeavor with your team. We will highly recommend your team to friends and family in search of incredible artistic imagery that captures genuine intimate life moments.
